data.description: Nestled within the highly sought-after Sarah's Crossing Development, this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Boasting a prime location in the esteemed Valley View School District, this residence presents an excellent opportunity for families or individuals seeking a tranquil yet convenient lifestyle. Key Features: Three bedrooms, two bathrooms, open floor plan with 12-foot raised ceilings in kitchen, breakfast area, and great room. Abundance of windows providing ample natural light, exterior clad entirely in brick. Master bathroom features bespoke tile shower, two sinks, soaker tub with tile surround, and extra-large closet. Hardwood floors in great room and hallway; tile in kitchen, bathrooms, and laundry area; carpeting in all bedrooms Granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms Crown moldings, ceiling fans, and pre finished wood shelving units in every closet. Gas fireplace for enhanced comfort and tranquility. Tankless water heater and energy-efficient foam-insulated ceiling.
